ou seek truth in small things.You live the each moment as if it''s unique.Love for nature.Love for life.Love for people.', 5421, 0), (21461, 'Enjoy every day and make each day great', 5422, 0), (21462, 'Do not wait for life. Do not long for it. Be aware, always and at every moment, that the miracle is in the here and now.', 450, 0), (21463, 'Do not do what you cannot continue to deliver.For, remember, the world wants to see a continuity of delivery of set standards...!', 4955, 0), (21464, 'When you want something, he entire universe conspires to help you achieve it.', 34, 0), (21465, 'Time is too short in this one life, to be able to do everything, but it definitely is long enough at least to be able to develop the will to do anything & everything...', 4955, 0), (21466, 'The challenge of life is regretless decision making, relentless pursuit of vision with faith, forgiving others, enduring pain with a smile & achieving goals with an extra MILE', 4955, 0), (21467, 'Nothing Comes Home...You Have To Get OUT & Get IT~!', 4955, 0), (21468, 'A sense of the divine presence and indwelling bears the soul towards heaven as upon the wings of eagles.', 771, 0), (21469, 'Once You keep Aside the Emotional side Of yours,Is when You stop using the phrase “This was a BAD PHASE” of life..', 4955, 0), (21470, 'Patience Pays..Is true! But the greater truth is that it takes advance payment before it pays you in return!', 4955, 0), (21471, 'A focused Mind is a result Of a little Effort To tell Your Distractions To sleep for A couple of hours While you are at WORK.', 4955, 0), (21472, 'Every comforting word is a command from a man of action...While every word of command is commotion from a man of just words...', 4955, 0), (21473, 'All have dreams, live for them, They add meaning to LIFE.The only thing that differentiates us from other beings is the fact that us can DREAM!!!', 4955, 0), (21474, 'The two toughest lessons to learn In life are “LET GO” & “LETs GO..!', 4955, 0), (21475, 'Have 